msgid "View publish preflight"
msgstr "查看发布预检"

msgid "Full duplicate-risk, SEO, and evidence details open in the preflight dialog."
msgstr "完整重复风险、SEO 和证据详情将在预检弹窗中打开。"

msgid "Check item"
msgstr "检查项"

msgid "Decision"
msgstr "结论"

msgid "Action"
msgstr "动作"

msgid "View details"
msgstr "查看详情"

msgid "No blocking or review-only checks."
msgstr "没有阻塞项或仅需审阅项。"

msgid "Only for publish decisions; Toolbox does not write WordPress fields."
msgstr "仅用于发布判断；Toolbox 不写入 WordPress 字段。"

msgid "Rerun preflight"
msgstr "重新运行预检"

msgid "Review overlap here, then use internal links only when you decide to cite an existing post."
msgstr "在这里审阅内容重叠，再只在决定引用旧文时使用内链。"

msgid "Passed checks"
msgstr "已通过检查"

msgid "No passed checks returned."
msgstr "没有返回已通过检查。"

msgid "No required fixes."
msgstr "没有必须处理项。"

msgid "No review-only checks."
msgstr "没有仅需审阅项。"

msgid "URL slug"
msgstr "URL 别名"

msgid "Q: "
msgstr "问："

msgid "A: "
msgstr "答："

msgid "%d possible overlap(s) found. Review these related posts once before publishing."
msgstr "发现 %d 个可能重叠的旧文。发布前集中审阅一次即可。"

msgid "If the draft repeats an older post, add a new angle or cite the old post instead."
msgstr "如果当前草稿重复旧文，请补充新角度，或改为引用旧文。"

msgid "More discoverability candidates (%d)"
msgstr "更多可发现性候选（%d）"

msgid "SEO title and description stay in the Core handoff section. Other SEO/AEO/GEO ideas are review notes only."
msgstr "SEO 标题和描述保留在 Core 交接区。其他 SEO/AEO/GEO 想法仅作为审阅备注。"

msgid "SEO Core review"
msgstr "SEO Core 审核"

msgid "Review the SEO title and description candidate before creating a pending Core proposal."
msgstr "创建待审核 Core 提案前，请先审阅 SEO 标题和描述候选。"

msgid "Article checkup"
msgstr "文章体检"

msgid "Check the full draft for sentence, fact-gap, tone, and structure issues without rewriting it."
msgstr "检查全文中的句子、事实缺口、语气和结构问题，不改写正文。"

msgid "Apply the reviewed SEO title and description through Adapter/Core. If policy blocks automatic execution, the proposal stays available for Core review. Toolbox does not approve, execute, or write SEO fields."
msgstr "通过 Adapter/Core 应用已审阅的 SEO 标题和描述。如果策略阻止自动执行，提案会保留在 Core 中供审核。Toolbox 不审批、不执行，也不写入 SEO 字段。"

msgid "Checks the full draft for review items and points you to affected paragraphs. It will not rewrite the article."
msgstr "检查全文审阅项，并指向受影响段落；不会改写文章。"

msgid "Review these full-draft issues manually. Toolbox points to paragraphs and editing direction, but does not rewrite or insert text."
msgstr "请人工审阅这些全文问题。Toolbox 会指出段落和编辑方向，但不改写或插入文本。"

msgid "No article checkup issues found."
msgstr "未发现文章体检问题。"

msgid "Review item"
msgstr "审阅项"

msgid "Evidence: "
msgstr "依据："

msgid "Clarity"
msgstr "清晰度"

msgid "Structure"
msgstr "结构"

msgid "Fact gap"
msgstr "事实缺口"

msgid "Format"
msgstr "版式"

msgid "Example: focus on structure and factual claims, not style preference."
msgstr "例如：重点看结构和事实主张，不看个人风格偏好。"

msgid "Paragraph %d"
msgstr "第 %d 段"

msgid "Paragraph is dense and may be hard to scan."
msgstr "段落信息密度较高，可能不便于快速阅读。"

msgid "Consider splitting the paragraph by claim, condition, or conclusion. Keep the editor responsible for the final wording."
msgstr "建议按主张、条件或结论拆分段落；最终措辞仍由编辑决定。"

msgid "One sentence carries too many clauses."
msgstr "单句承载的分句过多。"

msgid "Review whether the sentence should be broken into shorter factual steps before publishing."
msgstr "发布前请审阅是否需要把句子拆成更短的事实步骤。"

msgid "The paragraph contains a metric, comparison, performance, or scope claim."
msgstr "该段包含数字、对比、性能或适用范围类主张。"

msgid "Verify the source, test condition, comparison object, and applicable scope. Do not let Toolbox turn one observed result into a universal fact."
msgstr "请核实来源、测试条件、对比对象和适用范围。不要让 Toolbox 把一次观察结果变成通用事实。"

msgid "Tone may read stronger than the supporting evidence."
msgstr "语气可能强于现有依据。"

msgid "Review whether the claim should be softened or tied to a specific condition."
msgstr "请审阅是否需要弱化表述，或把主张绑定到具体条件。"

msgid "The article title is missing."
msgstr "文章标题缺失。"

msgid "Add a human-reviewed title before running title or metadata handoff actions."
msgstr "运行标题或元数据交接前，请先添加人工审阅过的标题。"

msgid "The article has enough body content but no excerpt."
msgstr "文章已有一定正文内容，但还没有摘要。"

msgid "Review whether a summary suggestion should be generated, then accept it manually before saving."
msgstr "请审阅是否需要生成摘要建议，并在保存前手动确认接受。"

msgid "Full article"
msgstr "全文"

msgid "The draft is long enough to need scan-friendly structure, but no obvious heading signal was found."
msgstr "草稿长度已经需要便于浏览的结构，但未发现明显标题信号。"

msgid "Review whether section headings, lists, or clearer paragraph grouping would help readers scan the article."
msgstr "请审阅是否需要增加小标题、列表或更清晰的段落分组，帮助读者浏览。"

msgid "No high-confidence local article issues were found."
msgstr "未发现高置信度的本地文章问题。"

msgid "This is a local heuristic check only. Run focused title, summary, taxonomy, internal-link, image, or publish preflight actions when needed."
msgstr "这只是本地启发式检查。需要时再运行标题、摘要、分类标签、内链、图片或发布预检等专项动作。"

msgid "Hosted AI reached the runtime but returned no paragraph-check text, so Toolbox showed the local no-rewrite fallback."
msgstr "托管 AI 已到达运行时，但没有返回段落检查文本，因此 Toolbox 显示了本地不改写兜底检查。"

msgid "Cloud marked this runtime response as omitted. Review storage mode, provider call count, and replay status below before rerunning."
msgstr "Cloud 将本次运行时响应标记为 omitted。重新运行前，请先查看下方的存储模式、提供方调用次数和回放状态。"

msgid "Cloud returned a runtime envelope, but no provider call was recorded for this request."
msgstr "Cloud 返回了运行时信封，但本次请求没有记录到提供方调用。"

msgid "The runtime returned a status but no displayable suggestion text. Rerun after adjusting the request, or use the local/full-article checks."
msgstr "运行时返回了状态，但没有可展示的建议文本。可调整要求后重新运行，或使用本地/全文检查。"

msgid "Runtime path"
msgstr "运行路径"

msgid "Hosted status"
msgstr "托管状态"

msgid "Cloud storage"
msgstr "Cloud 存储"

msgid "Provider calls"
msgstr "提供方调用"

msgid "Replay status"
msgstr "回放状态"

msgid "Idempotent replay"
msgstr "幂等回放"

msgid "Local fallback"
msgstr "本地兜底"

msgid "Run id"
msgstr "运行 ID"

msgid "Why no AI text appeared"
msgstr "为什么没有 AI 文本"

msgid "Runtime diagnostics"
msgstr "运行时诊断"

msgid "No runtime diagnostics returned."
msgstr "没有返回运行时诊断。"

msgid "Return to tool list"
msgstr "返回工具列表"

msgid "Tool list"
msgstr "工具列表"

msgid "No high-confidence local article checkup issues were found."
msgstr "本地启发式未发现高置信文章体检问题。"
